{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":842,"text":"What is a parent?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":3999,"text":"What is a parent?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7043,"text":"It's not an easy question."},{"time":9630,"text":"Today we have adoption,"},{"time":12028,"text":"stepfamilies,"},{"time":13628,"text":"surrogate mothers."},{"time":15846,"text":"Many parents face tough questions"},{"time":19151,"text":"and tough decisions."},{"time":21888,"text":"Shall we tell our child\nabout the sperm donation?"},{"time":27322,"text":"If so, when?"},{"time":29176,"text":"What words to use?"},{"time":31522,"text":"Sperm donors are often referred\nto as \"biological fathers,\""},{"time":37407,"text":"but should we really\nbe using the word \"father?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":41843,"text":"As a philosopher and social scientist,"},{"time":44272,"text":"I have been studying these questions\nabout the concept of parenthood."},{"time":49088,"text":"But today, I will talk to you\nabout what I learned"},{"time":52140,"text":"from talking to parents and children."},{"time":55377,"text":"I will show you that they know\nwhat matters most in a family,"},{"time":59755,"text":"even though their family\nlooks a little different."},{"time":63133,"text":"I will show you their creative ways\nof dealing with tough questions."},{"time":69287,"text":"But I will also show you\nthe parents' uncertainties."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75284,"text":"We interviewed couples"},{"time":76839,"text":"who received fertility treatment\nat Ghent University Hospital,"},{"time":81075,"text":"using sperm from a donor."},{"time":83183,"text":"In this treatment timeline,"},{"time":84774,"text":"you can see two points\nat which we conducted interviews."},{"time":88994,"text":"We included heterosexual couples,"},{"time":92055,"text":"where the man for some reason\ndid not have good-quality sperm,"},{"time":96435,"text":"and lesbian couples who obviously\nneeded to find sperm elsewhere."},{"time":102996,"text":"We also included children."},{"time":106878,"text":"I wanted to know"},{"time":108385,"text":"how those children define concepts\nlike parenthood and family."},{"time":114150,"text":"In fact, that is what I asked them,"},{"time":118259,"text":"only not in that way."},{"time":121437,"text":"I drew an apple tree instead."},{"time":125056,"text":"This way, I could ask abstract,\nphilosophical questions"},{"time":128427,"text":"in a way that did not make them run off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133332,"text":"So as you can see,"},{"time":135008,"text":"the apple tree is empty."},{"time":137630,"text":"And that illustrates my research approach."},{"time":140659,"text":"By designing techniques like this,"},{"time":142966,"text":"I can bring as little meaning and content\nas possible to the interview,"},{"time":148533,"text":"because I want to hear that from them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152362,"text":"I asked them:"},{"time":154738,"text":"What would your family look like\nif it were an apple tree?"},{"time":158739,"text":"And they could take a paper apple\nfor everyone who, in their view,"},{"time":162513,"text":"was a member of the family,"},{"time":164144,"text":"write a name on it\nand hang it wherever they wanted."},{"time":167342,"text":"And I would ask questions."},{"time":170153,"text":"Most children started\nwith a parent or a sibling."},{"time":173806,"text":"One started with \"Boxer,\""},{"time":176667,"text":"the dead dog of his grandparents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179830,"text":"At this point, none of the children\nstarted mentioning the donor."},{"time":184465,"text":"So, I asked them about their birth story."},{"time":189161,"text":"I said, \"Before you were born,"},{"time":191207,"text":"it was just your mom and dad,"},{"time":193594,"text":"or mom and mommy."},{"time":195421,"text":"Can you tell me how you came\ninto the family?\""},{"time":199282,"text":"And they explained."},{"time":201602,"text":"One said,"},{"time":203691,"text":"\"My parents did not have good seeds,"},{"time":206865,"text":"but there are friendly men out there\nwho have spare seeds."},{"time":211386,"text":"They bring them to the hospital,"},{"time":213160,"text":"and they put them in a big jar."},{"time":216249,"text":"My mommy went there,"},{"time":217510,"text":"and she took two from the jar,"},{"time":220786,"text":"one for me and one for my sister."},{"time":223725,"text":"She put the seeds in her belly --"},{"time":226161,"text":"somehow --"},{"time":228236,"text":"and her belly grew really big,"},{"time":230567,"text":"and there I was.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":233289,"text":"Hmm."},{"time":236123,"text":"So only when they started\nmentioning the donor,"},{"time":240215,"text":"I asked questions about him,\nusing their own words."},{"time":243926,"text":"I said,"},{"time":245349,"text":"\"If this would be an apple\nfor the friendly man with the seeds,"},{"time":249839,"text":"what would you do with it?\""},{"time":252069,"text":"And one boy was thinking out loud,"},{"time":254451,"text":"holding the apple."},{"time":255843,"text":"And he said,"},{"time":257890,"text":"\"I won't put this one\nup there with the others."},{"time":261239,"text":"He's not part of my family."},{"time":264191,"text":"But I will not put him on the ground."},{"time":266409,"text":"That's too cold and too hard."},{"time":269024,"text":"I think he should be in the trunk,"},{"time":272207,"text":"because he made my family possible."},{"time":275264,"text":"If he would not have done this,"},{"time":277242,"text":"that would really be sad\nbecause my family would not be here,"},{"time":281224,"text":"and I would not be here.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":285845,"text":"So also, parents\nconstructed family tales --"},{"time":289397,"text":"tales to tell their children."},{"time":292660,"text":"One couple explained their insemination"},{"time":295811,"text":"by taking their children to a farm"},{"time":299291,"text":"to watch a vet inseminate cows."},{"time":303656,"text":"And why not?"},{"time":305051,"text":"It's their way of explaining;"},{"time":307515,"text":"their do-it-yourself\nwith family narratives."},{"time":310981,"text":"DIY."},{"time":312533,"text":"And we had another couple\nwho made books --"},{"time":314925,"text":"a book for each child."},{"time":316752,"text":"They were really works of art"},{"time":318298,"text":"containing their thoughts and feelings\nthroughout the treatment."},{"time":322192,"text":"They even had the hospital\nparking tickets in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325553,"text":"So it is DIY:"},{"time":327198,"text":"finding ways, words and images"},{"time":329604,"text":"to tell your family story to your child."},{"time":333717,"text":"And these stories were highly diverse,"},{"time":336940,"text":"but they all had one thing in common:"},{"time":341913,"text":"it was a tale of longing for a child"},{"time":345885,"text":"and a quest for that child."},{"time":348370,"text":"It was about how special\nand how deeply loved their child was."},{"time":355142,"text":"And research so far shows\nthat these children are doing fine."},{"time":359814,"text":"They do not have\nmore problems than other kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362854,"text":"Yet, these parents also wanted\nto justify their decisions"},{"time":367299,"text":"through the tales they tell."},{"time":369505,"text":"They hoped that their children\nwould understand their reasons"},{"time":372663,"text":"for making the family in this way."},{"time":375865,"text":"Underlying was a fear\nthat their children might disapprove"},{"time":379843,"text":"and would reject the non-genetic parent."},{"time":382511,"text":"And that fear is understandable,"},{"time":385155,"text":"because we live in a very heteronormative"},{"time":388220,"text":"and geneticized society --"},{"time":390438,"text":"a world that still believes"},{"time":391954,"text":"that true families consist\nof one mom, one dad"},{"time":396130,"text":"and their genetically related children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399738,"text":"Well."},{"time":402165,"text":"I want to tell you about a teenage boy."},{"time":405290,"text":"He was donor-conceived\nbut not part of our study."},{"time":408658,"text":"One day, he had an argument\nwith his father,"},{"time":411300,"text":"and he yelled,"},{"time":413305,"text":"\"You're telling me what to do?"},{"time":415426,"text":"You're not even my father!\""},{"time":419601,"text":"That was exactly what\nthe parents in our study feared."},{"time":423984,"text":"Now, the boy soon felt sorry,\nand they made up."},{"time":427629,"text":"But it is the reaction of his father\nthat is most interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432169,"text":"He said,"},{"time":433772,"text":"\"This outburst had nothing to do\nwith the lack of a genetic link."},{"time":439765,"text":"It was about puberty --"},{"time":443005,"text":"being difficult."},{"time":444470,"text":"It's what they do at that age."},{"time":446792,"text":"It will pass.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":449462,"text":"What this man shows us"},{"time":451342,"text":"is that when something goes wrong,"},{"time":454564,"text":"we should not immediately think"},{"time":456189,"text":"it is because the family\nis a little different."},{"time":459330,"text":"These things happen in all families."},{"time":463936,"text":"And every now and then,"},{"time":465818,"text":"all parents may wonder:"},{"time":468412,"text":"Am I a good enough parent?"},{"time":471164,"text":"These parents, too."},{"time":473099,"text":"They, above all, wanted to do\nwhat's best for their child."},{"time":477748,"text":"But they also sometimes wondered:"},{"time":480034,"text":"Am I a real parent?"},{"time":482288,"text":"And their uncertainties were present\nlong before they even were parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486281,"text":"At the start of treatment,"},{"time":487737,"text":"when they first saw the counselor,"},{"time":490146,"text":"they paid close attention\nto the counselor,"},{"time":492865,"text":"because they wanted to do it right."},{"time":495853,"text":"Even 10 years later,"},{"time":498053,"text":"they still remember\nthe advice they were given."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504981,"text":"So when they thought about the counselor"},{"time":508854,"text":"and the advice they were given,"},{"time":510677,"text":"we discussed that."},{"time":511864,"text":"And we saw one lesbian couple who said,"},{"time":516627,"text":"\"When our son asks us,"},{"time":518255,"text":"'Do I have a dad?'"},{"time":521482,"text":"we will say 'No, you do not have a dad.'"},{"time":524839,"text":"But we will say nothing more,\nnot unless he asks,"},{"time":528287,"text":"because he might not be ready for that."},{"time":530339,"text":"The counselor said so.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":533350,"text":"Well."},{"time":535091,"text":"I don't know; that's quite different"},{"time":537017,"text":"from how we respond\nto children's questions."},{"time":540473,"text":"Like, \"Milk -- is that made in a factory?\""},{"time":543783,"text":"We will say, \"No, it comes from cows,\""},{"time":546969,"text":"and we will talk about the farmer,"},{"time":548749,"text":"and the way the milk ends up in the shop."},{"time":551806,"text":"We will not say,"},{"time":554102,"text":"\"No, milk is not made in a factory.\""},{"time":560042,"text":"So something strange happened here,"},{"time":562496,"text":"and of course these children noticed that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565571,"text":"One boy said,"},{"time":567445,"text":"\"I asked my parents loads of questions,"},{"time":569861,"text":"but they acted really weird."},{"time":572788,"text":"So, you know, I have a friend at school,\nand she's made in the same way."},{"time":577241,"text":"When I have a question,\nI just go and ask her.\""},{"time":581760,"text":"Clever guy."},{"time":583630,"text":"Problem solved."},{"time":585765,"text":"But his parents did not notice,"},{"time":588875,"text":"and it certainly was not\nwhat they had in mind,"},{"time":591481,"text":"nor what the counselor had in mind"},{"time":593439,"text":"when they were saying how important\nit is to be an open-communication family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600462,"text":"And that's the strange thing about advice."},{"time":602740,"text":"When we offer people pills,\nwe gather evidence first."},{"time":606536,"text":"We do tests,"},{"time":607816,"text":"we do follow-up studies."},{"time":609141,"text":"We want to know, and rightly so,\nwhat this pill is doing"},{"time":613092,"text":"and how it affects people's lives."},{"time":616035,"text":"And advice?"},{"time":618748,"text":"It is not enough for advice,"},{"time":620618,"text":"or for professionals to give advice\nthat is theoretically sound,"},{"time":625465,"text":"or well-meant."},{"time":627447,"text":"It should be advice\nthat there is evidence for --"},{"time":630852,"text":"evidence that it actually\nimproves patients' lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636174,"text":"So the philosopher in me\nwould now like to offer you a paradox:"},{"time":642308,"text":"I advise you to stop following advice."},{"time":647897,"text":"But, yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650221,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654591,"text":"I will not end here with what went wrong;"},{"time":657178,"text":"I would not be doing justice\nto the warmth we found in those families."},{"time":662931,"text":"Remember the books\nand the trip to the farmer?"},{"time":665585,"text":"When parents do things that work for them,"},{"time":669572,"text":"they do brilliant things."},{"time":672391,"text":"What I want you to remember\nas members of families,"},{"time":676058,"text":"in no matter what form or shape,"},{"time":678930,"text":"is that what families need\nare warm relationships."},{"time":685409,"text":"And we do not need to be\nprofessionals to create those."},{"time":689644,"text":"Most of us do just fine,"},{"time":692986,"text":"although it may be hard work,"},{"time":695038,"text":"and from time to time,\nwe can do with some advice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":699209,"text":"In that case,"},{"time":700504,"text":"bear in mind three things."},{"time":703760,"text":"Work with advice\nthat works for your family."},{"time":708008,"text":"Remember -- you're the expert,\nbecause you live your family life."},{"time":714681,"text":"And finally,"},{"time":716478,"text":"believe in your abilities\nand your creativity,"},{"time":721027,"text":"because you can do it yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725259,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726437,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}